                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--heading-color)] mb-4">Our Vision</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
                        To become the leading platform for event management, recognized for our innovation, reliability, 
                        and commitment to user satisfaction. We envision a future where organizing and participating 
                        in events is effortless, enjoyable, and accessible to all.
                    </p>
                </div>
